    "text": "Paris Climate Agreement Disclosure Act \n\nThis bill requires an issuer of securities to annually disclose information related to its greenhouse gas emissions, including whether the issuer has set emissions targets to comply with the goals of the Paris Climate Agreement and actions the issuer has taken or plans to take to achieve such targets."
